Hey, bud.

26:58.250 --> 26:59.420
What's going on?

26:59.420 --> 27:01.380
I don't want to
talk about it.

27:06.830 --> 27:09.460
All right. Well...

27:11.000 --> 27:12.420
...I'll just be here.

27:18.290 --> 27:19.880
What's wrong with Danny?

27:19.880 --> 27:21.790
I don't know.

27:21.790 --> 27:22.880
Well, I'll tell you

27:22.880 --> 27:24.080
