27:29.290 --> 27:32.120
Sorry.

27:32.120 --> 27:33.880
I'm sorry.

27:33.880 --> 27:36.580
Why?

27:36.580 --> 27:38.580
No, they're not coming in
for the surgery.

27:38.580 --> 27:40.880
I'd rather they come
afterward anyway.

27:40.880 --> 27:44.710
My mom can be a little...

27:44.710 --> 27:46.790
Uh, let's just say I'm glad
I'll be on painkillers.

27:48.790 --> 27:50.790
So, what's going on?
Did he say?

27:50.790 --> 27:52.330
Yeah, it's something
you said.

27:52.330 --> 27:53.750
Very funny.
No, I'm serious, D.

27:53.750 --> 27:56.290
It was something
you said.

27:56.290 --> 27:57.250
Did you tell them
they look cute together?

27:57.250 --> 28:00.290
Yeah,
because they did.

28:00.290 --> 28:03.170
Okay, well, apparently
Elliot is not as open

28:03.170 --> 28:04.290
with his family
as Danny is with you,

28:04.290 --> 28:06.330
so he was
a little freaked out

28:06.330 --> 28:09.380
that his buddy's mom commented
on his sexual orientation.

28:09.380 --> 28:11.170
Oh, God.

28:11.170 --> 28:13.790
You mean --
Yeah, that's right.

28:13.790 --> 28:15.120
You outed
a 12-year-old.

28:20.420 --> 28:23.040
Hey.

28:23.040 --> 28:25.830
Choosing Gary, I, uh,
think that meant a lot to him.

28:27.210 --> 28:28.580
It definitely
meant a lot to me.

28:31.080 --> 28:34.080
I knew Gary was probably
the right choice from the start.

28:34.080 --> 28:36.000
But to be honest,
the reason I, uh,

28:36.000 --> 28:39.120
didn't want him
is because...

28:39.120 --> 28:40.710
you did.

28:40.710 --> 28:42.920
Somewhere along the way,

28:42.920 --> 28:47.080
arguing against you
became my default.

28:47.080 --> 28:49.250
And that's not okay.

28:49.250 --> 28:52.000
Well, it's not like
I didn't deserve it.

28:52.000 --> 28:53.790
No, Eddie.

28:53.790 --> 28:56.500
I stopped giving you the benefit
of the doubt a long time ago.

28:58.750 --> 29:00.790
And that's on me.

29:00.790 --> 29:03.880
I need to take
some of the responsibility

29:03.880 --> 29:05.460
for where we ended up.

29:11.290 --> 29:13.330
It was
an honest mistake.

29:13.330 --> 29:16.120
And Elliot will bounce back.
Kids are resilient.

29:16.120 --> 29:17.330
