You're getting them through it.

29:42.960 --> 29:46.210
You're more than enough.
You don't have to be perfect.

29:46.210 --> 29:49.420
You just...
got to be there.

29:52.580 --> 29:53.920
Yeah.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.830
