-We're -- We're good.

30:59.710 --> 31:02.170
We're okay.
I'm -- I'm -- I'm good.

31:02.170 --> 31:04.380
We're all good?
Everyone's happy.

31:04.380 --> 31:06.580
Okay.

31:06.580 --> 31:08.380
Hey, so,
the butter you're eating?

31:08.380 --> 31:11.000
We make it in-house.
My apologies.

31:11.000 --> 31:12.170
