31:22.380 --> 31:24.290
That's what
embarrasses you?

31:24.290 --> 31:28.080
My depression that I'm trying
to do something about?

31:28.080 --> 31:31.040
This thing -- This thing that
I'm dealing with every day,

31:31.040 --> 31:32.460
and you throw it
in my face.

31:32.460 --> 31:34.170
And, oh, wait a minute,
Omar gets to drift through life

31:34.170 --> 31:35.580
like a damn prince!

31:35.580 --> 31:38.040
Don't you see
what you are doing?

31:38.040 --> 31:40.460
You made him what he is!
Oh, and what am I?

31:40.460 --> 31:43.080
-I can't believe you --
-Hi, again, table four.

