31:55.670 --> 31:56.830
was supposed to be
all about your bucket list.

31:56.830 --> 31:58.250
It ended up being
about everybody else.

31:58.250 --> 32:01.040
It's okay.
We got to spend the day

32:01.040 --> 32:02.290
with all of
our favorite people.

32:02.290 --> 32:04.500
We do plenty of that.

32:04.500 --> 32:07.420
We can go to Plymouth Rock
when I'm well again.

32:07.420 --> 32:10.170
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
When you're well again?

32:10.170 --> 32:13.580
Dr. Bloom, that sounds
awfully optimistic.

32:13.580 --> 32:15.000
I don't know.

32:17.420 --> 32:20.040
I've spent so long
living with death,

32:20.040 --> 32:22.580
I...it became a habit.

32:22.580 --> 32:24.790
But helping our friends today
made me realize

32:24.790 --> 32:29.170
that I really want to --

32:29.170 --> 32:31.790
I want to be there
to scream

32:31.790 --> 32:33.920
