wins Best in Boston,

32:33.920 --> 32:37.250
and I want to smoke a cigar
when Delilah's baby's born.

32:37.250 --> 32:38.880
And --
Don't do that.

32:38.880 --> 32:40.830
You're gonna beat cancer
and start smoking cigars?

32:40.830 --> 32:42.380
No.

32:42.380 --> 32:46.540
My point is my old bucket list
was about the past.

32:46.540 --> 32:50.080
My new bucket list...

32:50.080 --> 32:52.210
is about the future.

33:11.000 --> 33:14.210
All my life,
I have tried so hard

33:14.210 --> 33:15.710
